    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with supple leather seating that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key; it features a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from scheduled synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride. This is an excellent opportunity to own a high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
